<CONTENT id="_3793155_1"><TITLE value="Session 15"/><TITLECOLOR value="#000000"/><DESCRIPTION
   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;h4&gt;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46884678_1" alt="" width="715" height="379" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Introduction&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;div&gt;This brings the formal material for the Security Essentials course to a close.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;We will now spend some time summarising and reviewing the past semester's work.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;News&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46884679_1" alt="" width="455" height="238" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Australian cybercrime syndicate charged with laundering $1.7 million in stolen cash.&lt;br&gt;This group set up more than 80 bank accounts with stolen identities to transfer money out of Australia.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.proactiveinvestors.com.au/companies/news/1010230/australian-cybercrime-syndicate-charged-with-laundering-1-7-million-in-stolen-cash-1010230.html"&gt;Major Australian Cyber Crime Syndicate&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5 id="anonymous_element_24"&gt;Topic&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;These are the topics covered throughout the semester in this course:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46884680_1" alt="" style="border: 0px solid #000000;" height="553" width="576"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Also under 7. Cybersecurity frameworks - ISO 27001&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Review all these informative session pptxs &amp;amp; pdfs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-61980341_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Security Essentials 14 - CIS (1).pptx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371405_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;PROTECT - Strategies to Mitigate Cyber Security Incidents (February 2017).pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-61980342_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;SecurityEssentials 13 - NIST.pptx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371407_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;SecurityEssentials 12.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371408_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;ACSC Cyber Incident Readiness Checklist.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371409_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Security Essentials 11 - DataProtection.pptx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371410_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;27001 Cheat Sheet.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371411_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;CIA Session 10.pptx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371412_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Security Essentials 9.pptx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371413_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Security Essentials 8 Gaining_the_Advantage_Cyber_Kill_Chain.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371414_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Security Essentials 8.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371415_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Security Essentials 7 Security Tools, Platforms, and Services.pptx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371416_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;SecurityEssentials 6 - TPM.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371417_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Security Essentials - Access Control.pptx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371418_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Security Essentials 5.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371419_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Security Essentials 4 - IoT.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371420_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Security Essentials 4.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371421_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Security Essentials Session 3.pptx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371422_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Security Essentials Session 2.pptx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a alt="" href="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-55371423_1" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Security Essentials Session 1.pptx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Out of Session Activity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;The knowledge assessment is scheduled to be carried out next week.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;To prepare for this assessment:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;review your notes and powerpoints, and&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;read through your responses for PARTS 1, 2, 3, 4, and 5 for Assessment 1.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Portfolio Tasks&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Check assessments tab.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Complete and submit all outstanding work for Assessment 1.&lt;/div&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
